org.qdt.quingo.generator

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qdt.quingo.generator.Position

  • @Accessors
public class Position
extends java.lang.Object
    Record the position(s) of the newest data.

    This class is used as a field of MetaData class.

    Author:
    Jintao Yu
